Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.30,0:09:43.23,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(550,45)\fad(1500,0)}恋爱的\N\N最大幸福在于\N\N表白自己的爱。\N\N纪德（一八六九-一九五一  法）
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.76,0:09:45.79,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(510,125)}我的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.97,0:09:47.96,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(510,125)}名字是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.48,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(510,150)}日塔奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.59,0:09:53.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是位可怜非常的不来校学生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.24,0:09:56.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.29,0:09:59.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我自愿来校
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然这也是有原因的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.86,0:10:09.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没有人会可怜我…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.30,0:10:10.30,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(125,90)}可怜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.02,0:10:17.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么不因为担心而来我家看望我！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.14,0:10:19.18,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(500,105)}Question
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.10,0:10:23.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你谁
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.76,0:10:25.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是这个班级的学生啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.63,0:10:27.72,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(600,65)}Question
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.87,0:10:29.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很久都没来上课了哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.81,0:10:31.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这不是来了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.43,0:10:32.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天碰巧啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.93,0:10:37.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是…是吗  抱歉  我不是你们班主任啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.25,0:10:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那班主任去哪了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:40.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呃  这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.35,0:10:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师他上星期开始就不来校了…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.86,0:10:46.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？！  老师不来校？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:48.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近这事可不少见哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.42,0:10:52.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起学生不登校  老师不登校更加糟糕呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.51,0:10:54.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧  真让人捏一把汗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.98,0:10:55.72,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（担心×30  不要紧吧？）
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.72,0:10:58.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师把我晾在一边  自己却让人担心！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.39,0:10:59.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.38,0:11:04.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也罢  看了这个保证大伙会担心我！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.73,0:11:08.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.20,0:11:10.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了  那身伤…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.74,0:11:11.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要紧吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.81,0:11:12.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.19,0:11:15.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伤得好重啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.94,0:11:18.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事…摔伤而已
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.42,0:11:20.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摔倒可不会伤得那么严重哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.66,0:11:22.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传闻是遭受她父亲的DV哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:24.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,DV？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.04,0:11:26.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很让人担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.12,0:11:29.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,担心？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.46,0:11:31.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把我晾在一边  自己却让人担心！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.23,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(530,85)}疑似遭受DV少女
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.23,0:11:35.23,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(150,98)}小节浴
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.19,0:11:40.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家庭暴力(DV)什么的最近常有耳闻  已经不稀奇了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.14,0:11:45.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直不来上学还有更加严重的问题
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.30,0:11:48.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲生意赔本  房屋也被拿去抵押
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.17,0:11:51.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了躲避追债人  逃窜于四处的4张半榻榻米的小公寓之间
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.96,0:11:53.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,过着吃了上顿没下顿的生活…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.04,0:11:56.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全没有条件来学校…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:11:59.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,家境贫穷害你吃了不少苦呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.82,0:12:00.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:05.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日本真富饶  路上掉食物  没人会饿死
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.79,0:12:07.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过不可以捡地上的东西吃哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.06,0:12:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我饿了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.98,0:12:14.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这蘑菇  我们国家也有生长
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.83,0:12:16.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道哪个可以吃哪个不可以吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.96,0:12:18.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…不晓得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.38,0:12:20.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都有毒  都不能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.26,0:12:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我还是吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.20,0:12:28.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即便如此我还是吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.72,0:12:30.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃就得饿死…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.44,0:12:34.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我一起吃下蘑菇的伙伴们  有2人非常不幸地…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.01,0:12:36.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,够了  不用说了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:38.22,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(530,85)}难民少女\N\N（非法入境）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.22,0:12:38.22,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(175,97)}关内·玛莉亚·太郎\N\N（日本名）
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.22,0:12:40.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真让人担心啊  诶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.08,0:12:42.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又把我晾在一边  自己却让人担心！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.83,0:12:45.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  既然你们对我如此冷漠
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.41,0:12:46.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…我就使出最后的绝招！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.62,0:12:53.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…我还是死了算了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.97,0:12:54.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:55.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.87,0:12:56.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.11,0:13:10.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:12.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师你不是来校啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.95,0:13:14.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这人在干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.03,0:13:17.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如你所见  自杀未遂
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.21,0:13:18.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自杀？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:22.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,常有的事  你别放在心上
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊！  和我对视了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:28.18,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(530,85)}2年へ班班主任
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.17,0:13:28.18,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(220,90)}超消极教师\N\N糸色望
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.27,0:13:30.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就是我们的班主任哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.80,0:13:32.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班主任？  他？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:36.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吓坏了吧  本班净是些问题人物
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.61,0:13:38.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从老师开始就是这副德行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.22,0:13:40.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但值得庆幸的是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.59,0:13:42.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是如此普通
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.01,0:13:46.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通！？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.39,0:13:49.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通  普通  普通
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.16,0:13:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分之百用于贬义的「普通」！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.02,0:13:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀真好  小杏那么快就交到朋友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.50,0:13:59.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和美香要好不要好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:01.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很要好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.25,0:14:02.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和健太呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:04.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很要好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.50,0:14:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和奈美呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.56,0:14:07.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.57,0:14:11.62,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(550,110)}百分之百…\N\N百分之百用于贬义的\N\N「普通」！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.59,0:14:09.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分之百…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.22,0:14:10.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,百分之百用于贬义的…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.99,0:14:11.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「普通」！！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.64,0:14:13.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这漫画好看么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.24,0:14:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.22,0:14:15.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的女朋友可爱么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.01,0:14:16.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,普通
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.86,0:14:19.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这工作很「普通」啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.04,0:14:19.58,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（·不断被赶超的普通列车）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.58,0:14:20.11,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（·不便使用的FAX用普通纸张）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.11,0:14:20.65,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（·专科学校的普通学科）
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.80,0:14:22.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是「普通」！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.41,0:14:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是可怜的不来校少女！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:27.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说是说可怜的不来校少女…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.47,0:14:29.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过我看老师他也不怎么愿意来校的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.82,0:14:35.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老师我别说学校了  就连驾校都不去呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.74,0:14:38.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连驾校都不愿意去！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.46,0:14:43.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就连那个无论多危险的人最后总都能「顺利」毕业的驾校也？！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.29,0:14:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不如说那种人更容易通过考试
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.53,0:14:52.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顺便一提  藤吉的哥哥在萌萌木动画学院里还闹不登校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.12,0:14:53.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪壶不开提哪壶！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.37,0:14:55.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他可比你触目惊心得多了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:59.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,单纯的不来校缺乏冲击力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:03.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来你明明不来校  现在怎么又来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.65,0:15:05.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你不就成了来校学生了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:08.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要么承认自己是来校学生  要么不要来校  给我2选1！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.29,0:15:11.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事我最看不惯了  快给我分清楚！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.30,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(500,85)}一板一眼\N\N黏着质少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.30,0:15:13.30,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(150,99)}木津千里
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也是这个班级的学生吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.17,0:15:18.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幸好你足够普通
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.04,0:15:24.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这个班级已经有了31位…不…32位令人绝望的学生
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.55,0:15:26.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以称得上是绝望教室！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.24,0:15:32.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx95}顺带一提  被我刚才吐的血覆盖看不见的部分并非因为设定尚不完全…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.91,0:15:34.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不就是倒翻了咖啡吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.42,0:15:38.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么一提  周围的确有不少危险人物呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:40.68,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(475,99)}双重人格\N\N少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.66,0:15:40.68,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(160,93)}木村卡爱拉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.68,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(485,85)}毒舌短信\N\N少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.68,0:15:42.68,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(152,101)}音无芽留
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:44.68,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(465,85)}加害妄想\N\N少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.68,0:15:44.68,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(122,101)}加贺爱
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:46.68,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(280,85)}人如其名少女
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.68,0:15:46.68,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(152,101)}三珠真夜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:48.68,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(525,100)}网络偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.68,0:15:48.68,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(105,120)}小琴琴
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:50.68,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(530,60)}配对中毒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.68,0:15:50.68,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(150,105)}藤吉晴美
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.98,0:15:53.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来校算什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我来！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.73,0:15:59.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙  还不肯离校呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.57,0:16:01.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不离校？！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.74,0:16:05.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起不来校  不离校的人更麻烦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:07.10,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(470,60)}不离校\N\N校里蹲少女
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.10,0:16:07.10,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(150,105)}小森雾
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.12,0:16:11.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她已经蹲在这里拒绝离校很久了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.68,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(500,110)\fad(1000,0)}本不该相遇的两个人相遇了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.91,0:16:24.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也对…  正常考虑的话  你们2人是不可能相遇的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.94,0:16:28.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因为你来了学校  你们才会相遇的！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.00,0:16:33.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你像辻仁成的小说那样煽情也没用！！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:36.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不离校又怎样  不就是不离校么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:38.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不来校可是会形成社会问题的哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:40.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「不就是不离校么」？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.16,0:16:45.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小森同学  请你告诉这位同学不离校究竟有多可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.23,0:16:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然是老师您的要求…  好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.82,0:16:51.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟  你能否做到不离校呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.41,0:17:00.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能留在校内就算你赢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.40,0:17:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这有何难
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:09.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离校时刻开始播放的「梦幻曲」的旋律…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:12.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊——  老师已经有点想回家啦——
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.95,0:17:15.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很不安吧  心里没底了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有  这等小事…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.35,0:17:25.46,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身穿猫～儿～的皮大衣～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.69,0:17:29.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「梦幻曲」有过歌词么？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.57,0:17:33.05,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵妇人做了汤料理～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.38,0:17:50.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去往那老婆～婆也已经不～在那的住宅街～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.12,0:17:58.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身穿狗～儿～的皮大衣～
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.85,0:18:05.88,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贵妇人做了馅饼～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.27,0:18:18.63,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五金店的铲～子～卖得很～～好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:14.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么嘛！  这如同刀割内脏般的歌词算什么嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.68,0:18:17.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快疯了！  快疯了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.67,0:18:23.70,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卖出2把～之多～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.02,0:18:31.02,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用它挖～的洞够深～
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.20,0:18:32.90,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以将儿子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.01,0:18:35.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别擅自给「梦幻曲」作词！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.42,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(530,60)}超积极少女
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.42,0:18:37.42,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(150,105)}风浦可符香（P.N）
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.51,0:18:38.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是小森呀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.87,0:18:41.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是校里蹲的朋友？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.64,0:18:44.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小森才不是校里蹲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.22,0:18:45.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是座敷童子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.69,0:18:46.73,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(500,90)}全座联\N\N（全日本座敷童子联盟）\N\N正式会员
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.79,0:18:52.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多亏了小森愿意蹲进来  我们学校才能保持繁荣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.31,0:18:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让她离校的话  学校立刻便会走向毁灭
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.73,0:19:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事实上小森走出的以前的家  已经非常遗憾地毁灭了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.65,0:19:02.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.96,0:19:06.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小森是全日本座敷童子联盟的正式会员
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:09.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个合法的座敷童子  所以你大可以放心
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.98,0:19:12.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这…这孩子说什么胡话呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说…  你一来问题就越来越复杂了…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.32,0:19:16.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那咱回见！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.08,0:19:18.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:22.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这  这是！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.11,0:19:27.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黄昏时分  从住宅区飘来的咖喱香
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:31.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈～
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.84,0:19:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,操场上斜长的铁棒影子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:36.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动物们博取同情的叫声
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.74,0:19:40.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昏暗的走廊窗户中映照出疲惫的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.01,0:19:45.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别撑了  你还是快回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.27,0:19:47.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待会儿还有更难熬的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:52.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在一片漆黑的校内  还会看见源自恐怖猜疑的幻觉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.26,0:19:54.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撒谎  怎么可能会看见幻觉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.24,0:19:56.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧  老师
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.46,0:19:57.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唔…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.90,0:20:01.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身后有人！？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.32,0:20:05.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没人啊！  别…别乱讲！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.90,0:20:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才我确实看见了…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.70,0:20:10.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看  果然有人…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:12.15,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(500,60)}超·恋爱体质\N\N跟踪狂少女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.15,0:20:12.15,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(145,105)}常月缠
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.23,0:20:14.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啊  哪有？！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.22,0:20:15.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么你看不见呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.33,0:20:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道是  幽灵！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.86,0:20:23.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…我去外面呼吸一下新鲜空气
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.48,0:20:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好黑  好可怕  想回家！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:31.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比我想象中的要可怕许多啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.74,0:20:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的  不用害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.95,0:20:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为在这黑暗中并非我俩孤单二人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:41.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快看  小婴儿
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.96,0:20:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天花板上悬着婴儿的下半身！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.59,0:20:59.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我又不是你们的妈妈！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.88,0:21:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,绝对不是啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.93,0:21:03.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊～～
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:16.74,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(530,60)}普通少女
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.74,0:21:16.74,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(145,105)}日塔奈美
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.54,0:21:22.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是我的不来校经历
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.77,0:21:25.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是有这么回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.59,0:21:28.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日塔同学不来校的事我都彻底忘记了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.19,0:21:30.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:30.23,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(550,105)}嗯\N\N嗯\N\N一点没错
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.27,0:21:33.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么那么富有戏剧性的事你们也忘得掉！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.55,0:21:34.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.35,0:21:35.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.41,0:21:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为这事还算普通？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.93,0:21:40.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准说普通！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.70,0:21:42.70,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(420,54)}学号28号\N\N日塔奈美\N\N普通少女
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:15.66,zhushi1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\frz-90\pos(400,52)}本节目纯属虚构\N\N登场人物  组织名\N\N和HAMASHO\N\N无任何关联
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.24,0:23:18.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逝国
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.84,0:23:20.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过隧道，迎来隧道；
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.92,0:23:23.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过隧道，再度迎来隧道；
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.43,0:23:26.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过隧道，再度，再度迎来隧道；
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.15,0:23:28.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无限延伸的隧道，
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.22,0:23:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,隧道，还是隧道，
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.23,0:23:31.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的人生，
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.03,0:23:34.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿过隧道，迎来隧道。
